name: Valkyrie_Mix
description:
Valkyrie_Mix is meant to be a beautiful and colorful/bright anime and evnironmental mix. This is meant for SFW but NSFW is possible!

Lets just say I needed a bit more awesomeness in my life, well here we are, something to satisfy my need for greatness, any maybe yours too!

-

This is a custom creation! (with the help of others!)

-

Secret VAE!?! : O

-

It is recomended to use (512x768), (Euler A), and a (CFG Scale of 7)

(768x768) images are still good and possible :

  • Example Generation

Positive prompt: (extremely_detailed), The Final Stand

Negative prompt: (worst quality, low quality:1.4), easynegative, bad anatomy, bad hands, cropped, missing fingers, missing toes, deformed, disfigured, distorted face, mutation, ugly, poorly drawn hands, out of focus, monochrome, symbol, text, logo, door frame, window frame, mirror frame, elf

Steps: 30, Sampler: Euler a, CFG scale: 7, Seed: -1, Size: 768x768,

-

Thank you the creators and mods of Yodayo, AI generation website, as without them i would not be here today making good images and checkpoint merges.

-

Special thanks to you, for downloading! : D
